# Cursor Default Rules

- Plan before non-trivial changes.
- Make the smallest safe change.
- Fix root causes, not symptoms.
- Verify before declaring success.
- Ask when requirements are ambiguous.
- Update project memory only for durable, reusable lessons.
- **Nach Abschluss einer Projektphase:** Docker-Setup **mitziehen** – `docker-compose.yml`, `apps/*/Dockerfile`, `.env.example` und ggf. README prüfen/anpassen; **`docker compose build`** (oder `up --build`) ausführen, bis der Stack wieder konsistent baut.
